summary: Adds a player home for druids in the Falkreath Hold - Great for animal/garden lovers, people who like to live in nature. Includes: Chicken coop, Cow/goats, vegetable garden, alchemy/enchanting/smithing, diving board with pond and waterfall, wooded decor. Navmeshed for followers.
descriptionHtml:
Adds a player home for druids located in the Falkreath Hold, - Great for animal/garden lovers, people who like to live in nature. Includes: Chicken coop, Cow/goats, vegetable garden, alchemy/enchanting/smithing, diving board with pond and waterfall, wooded decor. Navmeshed for followers.

See screenshot for location.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Check out my other player home mods: 
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16143]Fire Dancer Retreat[/url] a mansion/manor in the reach with lots of features.

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16515]Windwood Redoubt[/url] a small fort for rouge characters. You can do what you want, be whoever you want, and you have excellent access to travelers on the road. 

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16604]Cuilalie Haven[/url] a scenic elven designed player home for the rangers/wood elves who like to be out in nature. Built like a tree house and surrounded by a trellis and the nature around you.
author: Cynster
